---
source: crates/zendriver-mcp/tests/schema_snapshots.rs
expression: "schema_for! (tools::find::BoundingBox)"
---
$schema: "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema"
title: BoundingBox
description: "Geometry wire shape mirroring [`zendriver::BoundingBox`].\n\nWrapped (rather than re-exporting the lib type) so it can derive\n`Serialize` + `JsonSchema` without forcing those derives on the lib's\ntype."
type: object
properties:
  height:
    type: number
    format: double
  width:
    type: number
    format: double
  x:
    type: number
    format: double
  y:
    type: number
    format: double
required:
  - x
  - y
  - width
  - height
